Author: ckaiycool
Post: https://forum.gimx.fr/viewtopic.php?f=9&t=3443
Game: Tomb Raider 2013
Platform: PS3
Device: Mouse/Keyboard
Playability: Average Input filtering 
Notes:
Change the In-game sensitivity in the gameplay options menu to 10.
This game has left stick intensity. Scroll the mouse wheel up or down to walk faster or slower.
Key Bindings: To get rid of confusion the keys [E] and [R] is same button, it is easier to press [E] when interacting. (This is because most games has that as [E] as the default button. And [R] is in most games Reload.)
https://strategywiki.org/wiki/Tomb_Raider_%282013%29/Controls
-->
